@startuml
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
autonumber

actor "Air Transport Company Collaborator" as ATCC
participant ":System" as System

activate ATCC

ATCC -> System : Requests to list company fleet

activate System
System --> ATCC : Requests company identification
deactivate System

ATCC -> System : Provides company identification

activate System
System --> System : Check if collaborator is authorized
System --> System : Validate air transport company
System --> System : Check if collaborator belongs to company
System --> System : Retrieve company fleet
System --> System : Prepare aircraft list with status

alt fleet has aircraft
    System --> ATCC : Display company fleet
else fleet is empty
    System --> ATCC : Display empty fleet message
else user is not authorized or company is invalid
    System --> ATCC : Display error message
end

deactivate System
deactivate ATCC

@enduml